author: rich
msg: - Fix for http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BEEHIVE-1004 : Unnecessary wrapping of Struts ActionForm in request

- Added a missing error page for NullActionOutputException.  This didn't cause any errors because the error page came from MissingActionOutputException (a superclass).  The new error page is more descriptive.

- Updated and added a few tests.  One of these is a test to ensure that the server is not in production mode when the tests are run, since several of our tests fail in production mode due to suppressed dev-friendly error pages and the like.
